name: (background)misty of forest 迷雾森林
description:
这个lora能为你提供迷雾森林的背景！推荐权重0.8左右，触发词是“misty of forest"对比图如下

This LoRa provides you with a background in the Misty Forest! The recommended weight is about 0.8, and the trigger word is "misty of forest", and the comparison chart is as follows

第一张是用我的T-anime-v2直接生成的图片，而下面是加了”<lora:misty of forest:0.8>,misty of forest“的图片，可以看到这个lora对于图片人物构图几乎没有影响，但是显著提高了背景和人物的光影

The first image is directly generated with my T-anime-v2, and the following is the image with "<lora:misty of forest:0.8>, misty of forest", you can see that this lora has almost no effect on the composition of the picture, but significantly improves the background and the light and shadow of the character
